ache is in-memory and fast.","version":854,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"#1e1e1e","index":"b5W","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BUT - If we shard a distributed cache by post \nID, we can still end up with a hot key \nproblem inside the cache itself. A viral \npost can overload a single cache shard, \neven though the cache is in-memory and fast.","height":125,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":646394136,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[{"id":"vK5pPzXa-ladkGNOnRdUA","type":"arrow"},{"id":"DGz1Z9o64_UDm_C6BZ38A","type":"arrow"}],"x":1243.1277212460514,"angle":0,"y":11180.257058131352,"width":474.69967651367188},{"seed":764953553,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"vqxY-3kVg2xe8gZcBC9F6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1776182896203,"locked":false,"text":"To fix this, instead of strict sharding, \nwe can use multiple independent cache \ninstances. The feed service randomly \nselects one of these instances when \nserving requests.","version":931,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"#1e1e1e","index":"b5X","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"To fix this, instead of strict sharding, \nwe can use multiple independent cache \ninstances. The feed service randomly \nselects one of these instances when \nserving requests.","height":125,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":363941400,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[{"id":"DGz1Z9o64_UDm_C6BZ38A","type":"arrow"},{"id":"baJmUIWSiIvtuCSahKeUZ","type":"arrow"}],"x":1242.6693531558562,"angle":0,"y":11365.430456359263,"width":389.15969848632812},{"seed":89286769,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"-bVKkSLOBt0H42qPfFYUW","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1776182896203,"locked":false,"text":"This spreads the traffic so that \ninstead of a single cache node \nhandling all requests for a hot \npost, the load is distributed \nacross n cache instances. Since \nn is small compared to total traffic, \nthis significantly reduces \npressure on both the cache and \nthe underlying database while \nkeeping the system simple.","version":721,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"#1e1e1e","index":"b5Y","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"This spreads the traffic so that \ninstead of a single cache node \nhandling all requests for a hot \npost, the load is distributed \nacross n cache instances. Since \nn is small compared to total traffic, \nthis significantly reduces \npressure on both the cache and \nthe underlying database while \nkeeping the system simple.","height":250,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":865061656,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[{"id":"baJmUIWSiIvtuCSahKeUZ","type":"arrow"}],"x":1654.4669853459795,"angle":0,"y":11535.141385977242,"width":356.55978393554688},{"seed":790428561,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"kWgq5PJ3SdU50VNk3Jp_D","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":{"mode":"orbit","elementId":"Qb3ZHq5OMTZ_KUvgmCpSB","fixedPoint":[1.0170648564883147,0.49866666666666182]},"endArrowhead":"triangle","fixedSegments":null,"opacity":100,"startIsSpecial":null,"updated":1776182896203,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[42,0],[42,-26.980602406306389],[221.67176821686326,-26.980602406306389],[221.67176821686326,15.019397593693611]],"endIsSpecial":null,"version":753,"elbowed":true,"type":"arrow","backgroundColor":"#1e1e1e","index":"b5Z","roundness":null,"height":42,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#1971c2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":{"mode":"orbit","elementId":"xxpDz-pa406QCDug6VK_h","fixedPoint":[0.49974285110696037,-0.04000